==花絮==
该片曾是一周的票房冠军，首日票房就破了100万元人民币。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2009-11-05/01442757102.shtml|title=《恋爱前规则》首日票房破百万 王珞丹拒绝转型|date=2009-11-05|accessdate=2014-04-04|work=新浪|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114457/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2009-11-05/01442757102.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2009-11-18/13212774343.shtml |title=《恋爱前规则》上周票房夺国产电影类冠军(图) |date=2009-11-18 |accessdate=2014-04-04 |work=新浪 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407081510/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2009-11-18/13212774343.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该片标志着王珞丹的转型，从天真浪漫到成熟稳重。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20091112/000102.htm|title=《恋爱前规则》全国热映 王珞丹转型惹争议|date=2009-11-12|accessdate=2014-04-04|work=腾讯网|archive-date=2014-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407103308/http://ent.qq.com/a/20091112/000102.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该片-{zh-hans:里;zh-hant:裡;}-，王珞丹出演的女主角“冉静”上演了“女追男”的故事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/i/2009-11-11/10152765629.shtml|title=《恋爱前规则》：倒贴女王珞丹顺利“脱光”|date=2009-11-11|accessdate=2014-04-04|work=新浪|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304133854/http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/i/2009-11-11/10152765629.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

